name: ncat-lib
description: Library of transformation modules used by the NCAT web based tool.
license.name: Other

name: HTDP
description: Horizontal Time-Dependent Positioning (HTDP) is a utility that allows users to transform positional coordinates across time and between spatial reference frames.
license.name: Other

name: xintg
description: xintg (INTerpolate Experimental Geoid) is used to interpolate the geoid height for a user specified position and geoid model.

name: inverse
description: The geodetic inverse, program INVERSE, is the tool for computing the geodetic azimuth and distance between two points, given their latitudes and longitudes.

name: forward
description: The geodetic forward, program FORWARD, is the tool for computing the latitude and longitude of a point, given the latitude and longitude of a starting point and the geodetic azimuth and geodetic distance between the points.

name: ngs_xml
description: Software to help with the creation of GVX (The GNSS Vector Exchange File Format) files utilizing the GVX_XML_Writer.
